HEADWORD: Kirghizia
<hw>Kirghizia</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A country in Central Asia,
formerly an Asian Soviet. It borders on Kazakhstan, Uzbekistan, China,
and Tajikistan.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Kirghiz, Kyrgyzstan, Kirghizstan.</syn>⟦br⟧
